*.vsix
node_modules/

# Build outputs of packages/vscode-extension/build-vendor.mjs.
# Source of truth for these lives in package.json (devDependencies),
# in the sibling `flatppl-grammars` repo (or the pinned remote tarball),
# and in packages/engine/ (the engine source). Re-run `npm run build:vendor`
# after dependency or engine changes.
packages/vscode-extension/lib/
packages/vscode-extension/grammars/
packages/vscode-extension/THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES.md

# Local symlinks created for the embed-test page (see
# packages/viewer/embed-test.html for the recipe). Source of truth
# is whatever the extension's lib/ currently builds — re-symlink
# after a `build:vendor` if needed.
packages/viewer/vendor/

# LLM input/reference files (kept in flatppl-design-llm/)
is-quality-llm*.md
